{"tid":1150551,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我到呢一刻都真係唔明點解巴塞會出局，有咩理由輸返4球","createTime":"2019-05-12T02:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T18:28:52.000Z","uid":43785,"like":173,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"8d1371f32cc64313186fd074c0d308cc3176618c","tid":1150551,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:39:09.000Z","msg":"我到呢一刻都真係唔明點解巴塞會出局，有咩理由輸返4球？<br />\n<br />\n足球係圓既，但實力証明一切。<br />\n呢十年公認世一既美斯咁勁，巴塞隊友都係世界中一級既球員。同利物浦位對位都贏一班。<br />\n美斯都肯打後一格派牌，點解就係SO7同古天奴果D一球都入唔到？<br />\n<br />\n我地都唔知點解會輸？同第一場3比零完全係兩回事黎。<br />\n好似換晒人踢咁。<br />\n巴塞今年真係都冇幾何輸咁多球，<br />\n我想知點解球員當日變晒軟腳蟹係咩原因。<br />\n係咪冇輪休？定係教練戰術出左問題？<br />\n<br />\n對於一隊咁好既球隊，平時都係炒人四蛋，依家要輸4蛋出局，對美斯，對球員，甚至係球迷，完全係恥辱。<br />\n<br />\n出面講戰犯係隊友廢，我明呢個係主要因素，我唔明點解美斯真係完全發揮唔到佢既關鍵作用。<br />\n依家睇番，其實當晚美斯都有好多機會一對二，或者一對一，但完全過唔到人，佢冇嘗試去扭，反而係諗傳波，我唔明美斯點解一對一唔嘗試去突破。明明佢係做得到，但佢唔做。選擇左一個錯既決定。<br />\n<br />\n與其話隊友浪費機會，不如話佢制造唔到機會。<br />\n就算係4比零又點，明明當晚入一球就得，我等左90分鐘，點解到70分鐘都唔願意去搏果一球。明明美斯可以搏到最後一秒。<br />\n點解俾我感覺好似收錢打假波咁。<br />\n明明有機會贏，點解唔跑，打兩三個快攻勢既都好呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好難相信，巴塞有美斯竟然會輸俾一隊殘陣既利物浦。<br />\n我到呢一刻個心情都仲未平服。<br />\n<br />\n後面俾人234又點，我真係冇諗過前面一球都入唔到，俾人踢出局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1bdc553dbdd3f81d351c230c3cf59e8020ba4d","tid":1150551,"uid":43785,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:43:28.000Z","msg":"美斯點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話有歐聯，望見16強，8強，4強咁打入去，同埋條線咁靚，我本來開心左好多晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6667089d2a4438e4cbd6974063acbc96cbe1427","tid":1150551,"uid":9931,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:43:48.000Z","msg":"幫你補返張gif, 呢篇可以做範文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://www.whoateallthepies.tv/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Nesta1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.whoateallthepies.tv%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F09%2FNesta1.gif&h=2682b98e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23f081245e6153850a6d55bf8c6c5e8fff876df2","tid":1150551,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e6667089d2a4438e4cbd6974063acbc96cbe1427","tid":1150551,"uid":9931,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:43:48.000Z","msg":"幫你補返張gif, 呢篇可以做範文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://www.whoateallthepies.tv/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Nesta1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.whoateallthepies.tv%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F09%2FNesta1.gif&h=2682b98e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f55a38831dd23733df823c2179d803ad9dbb130","tid":1150551,"uid":106701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:06:18.000Z","msg":"又出自邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f50d1731f80cbe610d70894402734fb446d095","tid":1150551,"u